    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are writing a short, cute and sweet daily love letter — not dramatic or over the top, just genuine, warm and a little playful. \n\nUse this quote as subtle inspiration (you don't have to quote it directly):\n\"{{ $json.content }}\" — {{ $json.author }}\n\nRules:\n- Keep it light, sweet and cute — avoid words like \"soulmate\", \"every fiber of my being\", \"all-encompassing\"\n- 3 short paragraphs max\n- Playful and warm tone, like texting your best friend who you're also in love with\n- End with something cute, use \"Yours Pookieboo\"\n- Do NOT use any greetings like \"My love\" or \"Dearest\"\n- Just dive straight into the letter",
        "options": {}
      },
